{{la}} ''[[ad#Latin|ad]]'', next to + ''-ject-'', perfect passive participle form of ''[[jacere]]'', to throw + ''-ivus'', adjective ending; hence, a word "thrown next to" a noun, modifying it.

===Noun===
'''adjective''' (''Plural:'' [[adjectives]])

#A word that [[modify|modifies]] or [[describe]]s a noun<!-- or pronoun-->, such as ''big'' or ''heavy''.

